Definitions

Patients are included in this list if they:

  • Have been identified to have started treatment in 2_treatment_initiation_début_de_traitement at any time prior to the end of reporting date, and

  • Missed an appointment within the reporting period, and

  • Have not been given an outcome that defines the end of follow-up (LTFU, death, transfer out) prior to the end of reporting date, and

  • Have not returned to clinic prior to the end of reporting date
